About

This 1970s Mid-Century Modern style bench has been completely restored. The comfortable seat is professionally upholstered in a dark grey mohair fabric with tufted details. The sturdy legs are three inches wide and made from steel with a chrome finish. This bench will make a great addition to any entryway or bedroom for years to come.
